SIZE=(23,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


                      Balance Option - Help

    Identifies the balance to use to determine a rate incentive.
    Valid entries are:
      C  Use the Combined Balance 1 on MICM Record 7101 (Model
         Definition) to calculate the rate incentive.

      D  Use the Combined Balance 2 on MICM Record 7101.

      E  Use the Combined Balance 3 on MICM Record 7101.

      F  Use the Combined Balance 4 on MICM Record 7101.

      G  Use the higher amount of the four combined balances.

      I  Use the individual account's balance defined in
         the Account Rate Balance Code on MICM Record 7102
         (RP Product Definition).
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M03050S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
